Error [ETYC0372177]: `_dynamic_call` cannot appear inside a conditional branch.
    --> compiler-test:4:20
     |
   4 |             return _dynamic_call::[u64](prog, net, func);
     |                    ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
     |
     = After flattening, `call.dynamic` results cannot be used in ternary operations. Move the `_dynamic_call` outside of the conditional block.
